Solid coding skills in Python/C/C++/Java;
Strong self-motivation and be able to work independently;
Strong communication skills, the ability to communicate effectively and manage relationships with stakeholders coming from both technical and non-technical backgrounds; and
Fluent in English, good written and oral communication skills.
